Marginal effects

x1x2 <- lm(data = df,
                  formula = 
                    wb ~ self_oriented + socially_prescribed)

x3 <- lm(data = df,
                  formula = 
                     x1x2[["residuals"]] ~ other_oriented)

summary(x3)
